Silicon Valley and the Pentagon

*Switching gears just a little bit, and going back to something you mention=
ed earlier. One of the common critiques of tech, or people that want to bri=
ng Silicon Valley to heel, is that it=E2=80=99s all downstream from the gov=
ernment, you only exist because of the government. You made this point befo=
